JS file:

const players = ["akshay", "amit", "vibhor", "vaibhav"];

const disp = (
`<article>
<h1>Players logged in.</h1>
<ul>
    ${players.map((loggers) => `<li>${loggers}</li>`)}
</ul>
</article>
`);

const yoyo = document.getElementById("yoyo");
yoyo.innerHTML = disp;

Html file:

<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width">
  <title>JS Bin</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Hello Guys</h1>
  <div id="yoyo">
  <div>
</body>
</html>

Output:

Hello Guys
Players logged in.
akshay
,
amit
,
vibhor
,
vaibhav
